\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 84. S. jailensis} Rubtsov, {\i Bjull. Gosud. Nikitsk. Bot. Sada}{\b  2}({\b 24}): 5 (1974). Densely-branched, glandular-pubescent small shrub; stems 10-20 cm. Leaves 3-4 cm, linear. Flowers solitary or sometimes paired. Calyx 20-25 mm. Petals white or yellowish. Capsule 8-10 mm, ovoid, more than twice as long as carpophore.{\i  Mountain rocks, c.} 1400{\i  m. Krym} ({\i near Gurzuf}). Rs(K).
