\pard\f0\fs28 Sect. SPERGULIFOLIAE Boiss. (incl. Sect.{\i  Suffruticosae} (Rohrb.) Schischkin and Sect.{\i  Macranthae} Rohrb.). Perennials with more or less woody stock and ovate, lanceolate or linear leaves. Inflorescence few-flowered or flowers solitary; flowers usually large. Carpophore well-developed.
\par

